{"tid":1622603,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"《不屈進行曲》英文歌詞 \"March of the Indomitable\"","createTime":"2019-10-04T16:43:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T19:33:52.000Z","uid":20035,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a1a73fa5c3d84b9920573b61b953ce01474c90e4","tid":1622603,"uid":20035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:43:25.000Z","msg":"我個朋友係英國讀緊Eng Lit PHD<br />\n想為香港出番少少力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以譯左呢個英文版本<br />\n我就冇能力錄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎各位巴絲攞去用！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢 首 係 戰 曲<br />\n今日港共政權已經完全失去合法性<br />\n臨時政府宣言已讀<br />\n香港人，反抗！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《不屈進行曲》<br />\n作曲: thomas dgx yhl<br />\n作詞 (中文): thomas dgx yhl, lk, 青棍幫, 眾連登仔<br />\n編曲: thomas dgx yhl , oldcaveman, octad, kotu, bp<br />\n <br />\nA1<br />\n來同行        看見嗎<br />\nMarch with us, can you feel<br />\n大地上       不屈的心<br />\nTh&rsquo; beatings of unyielding hearts<br />\n告眾義士   即使險惡<br />\n Spurring you on? Fear no peril,<br />\n也奮力 來驅走 昏暗<br />\nfight on, purge away the dim dusk.<br />\n<br />\nA2 <br />\n在黎明前   你聽見嗎<br />\nBefore the dawn, can you not hear<br />\n是濁霧下   鏗鏘吼聲<br />\nThe loud up-roar amid the mist<br />\n告眾弟妹   不屈的你<br />\nSpreading the fire? Bend not your soul,<br />\n會照亮明天的 香港<br />\nHeads up, to glisten our Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\nC1 <br />\n為大義  來一起奮抗戰<br />\nMarching on to lodge our righteous fight;<br />\n讓熱淚  和鮮血 沒白掉<br />\nWaste not drops of blood and spells of tears;<br />\n銘記  眾同伴獻身 約誓<br />\nForget not the will of whom we&rsquo;ve lost.<br />\n<br />\nC2 <br />\n願萬代  仍堅守這要塞<br />\nMay we guard this spirit with our lives;<br />\n讓願望  能歸依這家邦<br />\nMay our dreams be bricks for our Hong Kong;<br />\n在 絕地 屹立 共建光輝<br />\nStand tall, hold our hands, as one bright chain;<br />\n將正義    歸萬眾<br />\nMay justice be to thee."},{"pid":"776f4885ac3d8fa8ce171d8f6299324175e76ac9","tid":1622603,"uid":20035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:43:44.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"a6d65c69996c30d02589261f829672cc924b5e0d","tid":1622603,"uid":20035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:43:54.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"46b9841ff44bc4146a689cefa4297c9b6b451ea3","tid":1622603,"uid":20035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:44:04.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"ca1424337025bf6bb8d3e9a2183a46b48724d0e8","tid":1622603,"uid":20035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:44:14.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"17287decf8198e505fddba87035d78057ea8f29b","tid":1622603,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:44:22.000Z","msg":"［極重要］做嘢還做嘢，P牌仔想畀個革命方向大家討論討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1621742\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1621742</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bb304190abb378e6a8250a0e913582bb88c38e2f","tid":1622603,"uid":20035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:44:24.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"c794434ff6a9bbf068bbb66cb0f4d65b9bfc899f","tid":1622603,"uid":20035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:44:34.000Z","msg":"代"},{"pid":"6f605aaa70590da5c9ca1a76978d7f05041cc173","tid":1622603,"uid":20035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:44:47.000Z","msg":"革"},{"pid":"b8c447ea4cddcdf028f75cdb40543233c192b51c","tid":1622603,"uid":20035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"